                                                                                                                      - kind: Whitespace
                                                                                                                        text: " "
                                                                                                                      - kind: SubKeyword
                                                                                                                        text: Sub
                                                                                                                      - kind: Newline
                                                                                                                        text: "\r\n"
                                                                                                                      - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                                                                                                        text: "' This is a way to create a fhandler outside M2000 and pass it to"
                                                                                                                      - kind: Newline
                                                                                                                        text: "\r\n"
                                                                                                                      - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                                                                                                        text: "' M2000 system, creating a M2000 File Handler."
                                                                                                                      - kind: Newline
                                                                                                                        text: "\r\n"
                                                                                                                      - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                                                                                                        text: "' The M2000 File Handler now can be used from Print, Write, Input, Seek, Seek(), Get, Put, Close"
                                                                                                                      - kind: Newline
                                                                                                                        text: "\r\n"
                                                                                                                      - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                                                                                                        text: "' The exclusive or not is upon creation of the original file handler"
                                                                                                                      - kind: Newline
                                                                                                                        text: "\r\n"
                                                                                                                      - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                                                                                                        text: "' By Default we use open for Input (fway=1), so adjust it accordingly"
                                                                                                                      - kind: Newline
                                                                                                                        text: "\r\n"
                                                                                                                      - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                                                                                                        text: "' The fstep say 1 (means one character, this can change to something else only for Field type,fway=4)"
                                                                                                                      - kind: Newline
                                                                                                                        text: "\r\n"
                                                                                                                      - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                                                                                                        text: "' The unic=1 means we use UTF16LE (One Word width, 2 bytes)"
                                                                                                                      - kind: Newline
                                                                                                                        text: "\r\n"
                                                                                                                      - kind: EndOfLineComment
                                                                                                                        text: "' Use unic=0 for ANSI (is bound to Locale number)"
                                                                                                                      - kind: Newline
                                                                                                                        text: "\r\n"
                                                                                                                      - kind: Newline
                                                                                                                        text: "\r\n"
